{"tid":941712,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁攰","createTime":"2018-12-15T05:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T05:28:54.000Z","uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c3cb3c4eeb4479a5904b9764b9517615bc1132","tid":941712,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T05:05:17.000Z","msg":"識佢半年，一齊左3個月，同佢一齊好開心，覺得同佢好岩，但突然屋企發生左d 事，抽唔到好多時間陪佢，但一有時間我就搵佢，但點解有一日佢突然消失左緊，幾日搵佢唔到，係咩都搵佢唔到，一句話都唔留，封我電話同whatapp,去佢家門口等，又等唔到佢，日日都搵，一星期後佢突然搵返我，我即刻衝左去見佢，問佢咩事，佢咩都唔講唔答，話好難講，但我太鐘意佢，我冇迫佢，見完都好地地，但之後又開始冇點回我，同之前唔同曬，我要點做了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屋企又有事，佢又咁樣，我好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ac33ce471f7abfe304b460370bc905428deb8e","tid":941712,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"完了"},{"pid":"9211b271e69027f964d4a6ad285d442d01f91a65","tid":941712,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T05:24:13.000Z","msg":"🙂"},{"pid":"2388ced2baeb0de5bacf7fc5fad029fc1e695f9c","tid":941712,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ac33ce471f7abfe304b460370bc905428deb8e","tid":941712,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"完了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"講就易 做好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}